<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.9">
<l>pulamaṉu malarmicai malarmakaḷ puṇariya</l>
<l>nilamaka ḷeṉaviṉa makaḷirka ḷivaroṭum</l>
<l>valamaṉu paṭaiyuṭai maṇivaṇar nitikuvai</l>
<l>kalamaṉu kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god, the jewel-hued one with a weapon fixed at his right,</l>
<l>With the attendant ladies called lady earth in the company of</l>
<l>The lady of the blossom on a blossom where the senses stay fixed,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram where anchor ships with piles of treasure.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
